---
layout: base.njk
title: About
isAboutPage: true
---
<div class="about-page wrapper">
  <h1>About This Site</h1>

  <p>{{ site.descriptionHtml | safe }}</p>

  <p>This site was created in order to more easily explore the podcast. While Apple Podcast and YouTube do provide transcripts, as of this writing in 2026, it is not possible to search <i>across</i> episodes.</p>

  <p>Listen and follow Roaming Holiday at <a href="https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/roaming-holiday/id1708646675">Apple Podcasts</a>, <a href="https://open.spotify.com/show/3SxMKIOKJwbgUs3fbwSncD">Spotify</a>, <a href="https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLHsvN4hgousAB1aBl-dDwIs_JaBMGMvQd">YouTube</a>, and other platforms.</p>

  <aside class="roaming-by-numbers">
    <h2>Roaming by Numbers</h2>

    <section>
      <h3>Podcast Stats</h3>
      <dl>
        <dt>Total episodes</dt>
        <dd>{{ stats.totalEpisodes }} episodes</dd>

        <dt>Total length</dt>
        <dd>{{ stats.totalDurationSeconds | formatRoundedHuman }}</dd>

        <dt>Average episode length</dt>
        <dd>{{ stats.averageEpisodeDurationSeconds | formatRoundedHuman }}</dd>

        <dt>Longest episode</dt>
        <dd><a href="{{ stats.longestEpisode.url }}">{{ stats.longestEpisode.title }}</a> ({{ stats.longestEpisode.durationSeconds | formatRoundedHuman }})</dd>

        <dt>Shortest episode</dt>
        <dd><a href="{{ stats.shortestEpisode.url }}">{{ stats.shortestEpisode.title }}</a> ({{ stats.shortestEpisode.durationSeconds | formatRoundedHuman }})</dd>
      </dl>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h3>Transcription Stats</h3>
      <dl>
        <dt>Transcribed episodes</dt>
        <dd>{{ stats.totalTranscribedEpisodes }} episodes</dd>

        <dt>Total transcribed words</dt>
        <dd>{{ stats.totalTranscribedWordCount | formatNumber }} words</dd>

        <dt>Average words per episode</dt>
        <dd>{{ stats.averageTranscribedEpisodeWordCount | formatNumber }} words</dd>

        <dt>Wordiest episode</dt>
        <dd><a href="{{ stats.wordiestEpisode.url }}">{{ stats.wordiestEpisode.title }}</a> ({{ stats.wordiestEpisode.wordCount | formatNumber }} words)</dd>

        <dt>Tersest episode</dt>
        <dd><a href="{{ stats.leastWordiestEpisode.url }}">{{ stats.leastWordiestEpisode.title }}</a> ({{ stats.leastWordiestEpisode.wordCount | formatNumber }} words)</a></dd>

        <dt>Most fucks given</dt>
        <dd><a href="{{ stats.mostFucks.url }}">{{ stats.mostFucks.title }}</a> ({{ stats.mostFucks.wordCount | formatNumber }} fucks)</dd>
      </section>
  </aside>

  <p><a href="/">Return to home</a></p>
</div>
